    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_main-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（次のトリエルの仕事は、瑠依・優・すみれ）\n（三人が共演する、新しいミュージカルへの出演だ）",
      "startTime": 4.924709918,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4241.9567486999995,
          "startTime": 9.1666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん、今日も稽古の差し入れ\nありがとうございます。いつから見てはったんです？",
      "startTime": 13.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "だいぶ前から見ていたけど、俺に全然気付かなかったな\nその集中力も凄いし、何より優の仕上がりに驚いたよ",
      "startTime": 21.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "今までのステージはもちろん、演技の仕事や\nバラエティでの経験まで活かされてるように感じる",
      "startTime": 29.616530396,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、今回はミュージカルやから、演技は当然\n歌もダンスもライブ感も、全部大事にしたいんです",
      "startTime": 38.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "今回の舞台は、三人ともメインキャストだよな\nファンタジー系の台本も凄く面白かったよ",
      "startTime": 46.5738474168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ。話の舞台は、宝石の体と永遠の命を持つ者達の国\nうちとすみれちゃんは、その国のお姫様姉妹なんです",
      "startTime": 56.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "そこに、人間の瑠依ちゃんが訪れてきて………\n命とか人生の意味を考えさせる、深いテーマ性の作品で",
      "startTime": 65.155982431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "役柄にも舞台にも、すごーく理解度が求められて\nうちら三人とも、毎日ひぃひぃ言うてお稽古してます",
      "startTime": 75.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……なんて言ってるわりには、平気そうだな\n大変そうな舞台だから心配してたんだが、安心したよ",
      "startTime": 83.4333424886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、やっとうちが演じるお姫様の気持ちが掴めてきて\n今は大変さより楽しさの方がずっと上なんです",
      "startTime": 92.6333424886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "難しい役やけど、うちらは全力でやり遂げてみせます\nうちら、何度でも挑戦と成長を続けるグループですから",
      "startTime": 102.7000091553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、今のトリエルには余計な心配だったみたいだ\n……ところで、そんな優に新しい仕事の依頼なんだが",
      "startTime": 111.9000091553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "そんなら、着替えてから話聞かせて下さい\n……汗、一杯かいてしもて",
      "startTime": 120.666675822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、舞台の告知のお仕事……ですか\nほんなら番組出演とか、雑誌のインタビューやろか",
      "startTime": 131.6193110124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ。テレビ番組への出演ではあるんだが……\nいろいろと難しそうで、正直受けるか悩んでいてな",
      "startTime": 139.7275265456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "その、優に出演してほしいのは……\nお笑い番組、なんだ",
      "startTime": 147.1226779175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "おわらい……ばんぐみ？　ちょっと待って下さい\nうちがお笑い番組なんて出たら……",
      "startTime": 155.0000111898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、分かってる。やっぱりアイドルに頼む仕事じゃ\nないよな。もっと別の告知の仕方を相談して――",
      "startTime": 161.2666829427,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "うち、お笑い事務所にスカウトされてしまいます！\nそうなったら、トリエルは一体どうなってまうん！？",
      "startTime": 169.0333496094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "…………ん？　待て待て\n優、一体何を言ってるんだ？",
      "startTime": 174.7781207115,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、うちがお笑いの研究\nしてること、いつから気付いてはったんです！？",
      "startTime": 179.9856267572,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "いや、今教えられて知ったんだけど……それはさておき\n優はお笑い番組に出るのが嫌、って訳じゃないのか？",
      "startTime": 187.6000305176,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "嫌な訳ありません。まさかうちにお笑いのお仕事が\n舞い込んでくるなんて……これも運命、なんかな",
      "startTime": 195.9666971843,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "意外にも乗り気だな……。それにしても\n優がそんなにお笑いが好きなんて知らなかったよ",
      "startTime": 204.9000305176,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "少し前『ある人を爆笑させる』って課題に挑んだんです\nその時のうちのお笑いは、まだまだ拙くて",
      "startTime": 213.6000172933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "何度もスベりながら、もう最後は開き直って勢いだけで\nいったんやけど、笑顔が見れた時はほんまに嬉しくて",
      "startTime": 222.5850489598,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-yu016.m4a",
      "text": "人を笑わせるってこんなに気持ちいいんや、って改めて\n知って。それがきっかけでお笑いにのめり込んだんです",
      "startTime": 232.36668396,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "（優は一度興味を持ったら、とことんハマるタイプだな）\n（オタク気質とでもいうんだろうか）",
      "startTime": 241.7000172933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_15_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、優が乗り気なら、番組出演の話は進めていいか？\nちなみに、今のところスカウトの話は来ていないが……",
      "startTime": 249.4333506267,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
